  <brief_title>Sublingual Misoprostol in Decreasing Blood Loss Prior to Myomectomy</brief_title>
  <acronym>SL-MISO</acronym>
  <official_title>Single Dose Versus Two Doses of Sublingual Misoprostol in Decreasing Blood Loss Prior to Abdominal Myomectomy: A Randomized Double-blinded Clinical Trial</official_title>
