  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to compare the effectiveness of sublingual administered prostaglandin
      E1 synthetic analogue (misoprostol) 400 microgram versus placebo before myomectomy to
      decrease blood loss during and after the operation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
